c: 7
v: 137
t: "Men ronini yimЙ“e wonanooЙ“e lo'ineede Й“en fuЙ—naange leydi ndin e hiirnaange mayri ndi Men barkini e mu'un. Konngol Joomi maa moЖҙЖҙongol ngol timmii e Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en sabu ko Й“e muГұГұinoo kon. Men halki ko Fir'awna e yimЙ“e mun Й“en moЖҙЖҙinanynoo, e kon ko Й“e Й“amtaynoo (e kuЙ“eeje)"